子</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 2023 年雷丁和利兹禁止篝火、烧烤和一次性电子烟https://www.nme.com/news/music/campfires-bbqs-and-disposable-vapes-banned-from-reading-leeds-2023-3477632?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=campfires-bbqs-and-disposable- 2023 年雷丁利兹电子烟禁令Tom SkinnerThu, 03 Aug 2023 10:02:24 +0000 FestivalsMusic NewsNewsReading & Leeds FestivalReading https://www.nme.com/?p=3477632 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利兹音乐节主舞台" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这两个节日将于本月晚些时候回归</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/campfires-bbqs-and-disposable-vapes-banned-from-reading-leeds-2023-3477632">2023 年雷丁和利兹禁止篝火、烧烤和一次性电子烟的</a>消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="利兹音乐节主舞台" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/leeds-main-stage-2022-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在本月双节回归之前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/reading-festival-2022">雷丁和利兹</a>已禁止篝火、烧烤和一次性电子烟。</p><p> 2023 年的该活动将于 8 月 25 日至 27 日在雷丁的里奇菲尔德大道和利兹的布拉汉姆公园举行。您可以<a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/reading-and-leeds-festival?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=TUeRTURCWxyNT8CXSVXWIUg%3AUkF11-2OiX3SU00&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里购买剩余的门票</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/reading-festival-2022-review-arctic-monkeys-the-1975-3300010">2022 年读书节回顾：巨星头条人物震撼夏季庆典结束</a></strong></li></ul><p>今年 R&amp;L 的主角将是<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billie-eilish">Billie Eilish</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sam-fender">Sam Fender</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-1975">The 1975</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-killers">The Killers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foals">Foaals</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/imagine-dragons">Imagine Dragons</a> 。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2023-joel-dommett-russell-kane-and-fern-brady-lead-alternative-stage-line-up-3471914">该系列产品</a>中还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wet-leg">Wet Leg</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/central-cee">Central Cee</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/inhaler">Inhaler</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/steve-lacy">Steve Lacy</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/knucks">Knucks 等</a>。</p><p>距离节日大门开放仅剩三周时间，组织者已与节日观众分享了一些<a href="https://www.readingfestival.com/information-category/the-essentials?_gl=1*tv9rh4*_up*MQ..*_ga*MjA0MDQyMTQ5NS4xNjkwNTU1ODg3*_ga_9KNDL1VVS6*MTY5MDU1NTg4Ni4xLjEuMTY5MDU1NTk3Ni4wLjAuMA.." target="_blank" rel="noopener">“基本信息”</a> ，其中重点介绍了 2023 年新禁止的物品。</p><p>雷丁和利兹现在不允许在现场使用一次性电子烟。清单上写道：“它们会污染环境，如果在废物处理中心处理不当，可能会造成危险。”</p><p>此外，“节日期间的任何地方，包括露营地”都禁止使用篝火和一次性烧烤设施。组织者在解释这一禁令时表示：“这是为了支持《 <a href="https://ldcommunications.us19.list-manage.com/track/click?u=5fc0ac914df332a4d84576a30&amp;id=c3b1016f52&amp;e=bd03099d6b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">空气质量行动计划》</a> ，并考虑到我们的<a href="https://ldcommunications.us19.list-manage.com/track/click?u=5fc0ac914df332a4d84576a30&amp;id=945ad83757&amp;e=bd03099d6b" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《绿国宪章》</a>中规定的当地影响。”</p><p> “任何看到生火或助长火势或一次性烧烤的人都将被逐出节日场地。我们必须继续保护我们在这个星球上的未来。”</p><p>进入竞技场的每人还限制携带一件 A4 尺寸的行李（8.27 英寸 x 11.69 英寸）。您可以<a href="https://www.readingfestival.com/information-category/the-essentials?_gl=1*tv9rh4*_up*MQ..*_ga*MjA0MDQyMTQ5NS4xNjkwNTU1ODg3*_ga_9KNDL1VVS6*MTY5MDU1NTg4Ni4xLjEuMTY5MDU1NTk3Ni4wLjAuMA.." target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>找到违禁物品的完整列表。 </p><figure id="attachment_3300774" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3300774" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3300774" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022.jpg" alt="读书节主舞台" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/08/reading-main-stage-2022-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3300774" class="wp-caption-text">读书节主舞台。图片来源：Joseph Okpako/WireImage</figcaption></figure><p>此外，到 2023 年，R&amp;L 将这两个地点的环保露营地的容量增加了两倍。露营区也引入了“AIR Hubs”，与现有的安全和管理团队一起提供援助、信息和响应设施。</p><p>这些中心的工作人员将由 WAVES、Street Pastors、Salvation Army、Number 5 Counwriting、Mind、CGL、RBFRS、SoulScape 和 Oxfam 等团体组成，从周三到周一提供 24/7 全天候支持。</p><p>清单上写道：“露营区设有 16 个 AIR Hub，节日观众永远不会远离友好的支持。”</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-replace-lewis-capaldi-reading-leeds-2023-3466700">The 1975 取代刘易斯·卡帕尔迪 (Lewis Capaldi) 加入雷丁和利兹 2023 年阵容</a>。<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/matty-healy">马蒂·希利</a>等人将为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-1975-announce-10th-anniversary-reissues-and-merch-bundles-for-self-titled-debut-album-3476627">他们2013年的首张同名专辑</a>举办“十周年纪念演出”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-1975-reading-festival-2022-review-photos-setlist-3300042">就在去年，这支曼彻斯特乐队在 R&amp;L 音乐节上名列前茅</a>，当时<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/reading-leeds-2022-the-1975-replace-rage-against-the-machine-as-headliners-3288739">他们在最后一刻取代了 Rage Against The Machine</a> 。 1975 年的音乐节首次成为 2019 年双节的主角。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/campfires-bbqs-and-disposable-vapes-banned-from-reading-leeds-2023-3477632">2023 年雷丁和利兹禁止篝火、烧烤和一次性电子烟的</a>消息首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
西蒙·佩吉透露了他最喜欢的《Cornetto》三部曲中的电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/simon-pegg-reveals-his-favourite-film-in-the-cornetto-trilogy-3477613?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=simon-pegg-reveals-his-短号三部曲中最喜欢的电影Chris EdwardsThu, 03 Aug 2023 09:46:56 +0000 Film NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3477613 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西蒙·佩吉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “这是对观众最不友好的”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/simon-pegg-reveals-his-favourite-film-in-the-cornetto-trilogy-3477613">西蒙·佩吉 (Simon Pegg) 在《Cornetto》三部曲中透露了他最喜欢的电影，这篇文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="西蒙·佩吉" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Simon-Pegg-main-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/simon-pegg">西蒙·佩吉</a>透露了他最喜欢的《三味科尔内托》三部曲中的电影。</p><p>由<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/edgar-wright">埃德加·赖特 (Edgar Wright)</a>执导的备受喜爱的三部电影包括僵尸喜剧《<em>僵尸肖恩》</em> （草莓）、动作喜剧<em>《热血警探》</em> （经典）和科幻喜剧<em>《世界的尽头》</em> （薄荷）。</p><p>现在，佩吉透露了这三部电影中他最喜欢哪一部。</p><div class="css-c2lb2p"><p> “你知道，《科内托》三部曲中我最喜欢的是<em>《世界的尽头》</em> ，因为它对观众最不友好，”这位<em>《碟中谍》</em>明星告诉<em><a href="https://discussingfilm.net/2023/07/31/simon-pegg-talks-mission-impossible-next-edgar-wright-collaboration-exclusive-interview" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Discussing Film</a></em> 。 </p><figure id="attachment_3359801" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3359801" style="width: 1940px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-3359801 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360.jpg" alt="世界尽头" width="1940" height="1240" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360.jpg 1940w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-400x256.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-800x511.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-696x445.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-1392x890.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-1068x683.jpg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-300x192.jpg 300w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-768x491.jpg 768w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/12/The-Worlds-End-main-e1691054959360-1536x982.jpg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1940px) 100vw, 1940px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3359801" class="wp-caption-text"> 《世界的尽头》中的尼克·弗罗斯特、西蒙·佩吉和帕迪·康斯戴恩 图片来源：Alamy</figcaption></figure></div><div class="css-12zje5r"><p> “这是三者中最黑暗的一个。这是最具挑战性的，我喜欢这样的想法：让观众感到有点不舒服，但不一定对熟悉的东西感到舒服。”</p><p>佩吉在采访中还透露，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/simon-pegg-making-new-film-with-edgar-wright-3476513">他和赖特目前正在一起规划他们的下一个项目</a>。</p></div><div class="css-12zje5r"><p> “我们一直在做原创的想法，尽管我们是围绕现有的类型或其他东西来构建它们的。埃德加和我总是谈论我们下一步要做什么。我们都不敢相信<em>世界末日已经过去十年了，”</em>他说。</p></div><div class="css-12zje5r"><p> “我要说的是，这不是我们是否会做某事的问题，而是我们<em>何时</em>做某事的问题，我们会这么做，因为我们已经开始谈论它了。”</p><p>佩吉继续说道：“埃德加去年来到我家，我们开始讨论想法。这不会是另一种科内托电影，因为这些电影是专门的类型即兴表演，解决了集体与个人的想法。</p><p> “对于接下来要做的事情，我们希望与此完全不同。我们不想拍动作片、科幻片或恐怖片。我们想要制作一部完全属于自己的电影，存在于科内托三部曲之外。事实上，我的愿望是做一些超级不同的事情。” </p><figure id="attachment_2513468" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2513468" style="width: 1494px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2513468" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz.jpg" alt="" width="1494" height="1000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz.jpg 1494w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz-696x466.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz-1392x932.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz-400x268.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz-800x535.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/06/Hot-Fuzz-1068x715.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 1494px) 100vw, 1494px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2513468" class="wp-caption-text">尼克·弗罗斯特和西蒙·佩吉在《热血警探》中。图片来源：环球影业</figcaption></figure><p>这位演员接着强调，他们的下一个项目不会是另一部科内托电影。</p><p>他说：“冒着让人们失望的风险，我们收到了很多要求‘平衡’这三部电影的请求。我觉得人们拥抱熟悉并再次接受同样的事情是一种懒惰的冲动。</p><p> “我对此感到非常受宠若惊，当人们说‘哦，我们希望看到更多’时，这绝对是一种启发。”我明白了！但我们真正需要的是新的东西。我们需要新的想法。我们需要接受挑战。”</p><p>在其他地方，佩吉最近讨论了人工智能在电影行业中日益流行的问题，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/simon-pegg-ai-push-humans-up-our-game-3470061">表明它可以推动人类“提高我们的游戏水平”</a> 。</p></div><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/simon-pegg-reveals-his-favourite-film-in-the-cornetto-trilogy-3477613">西蒙·佩吉 (Simon Pegg) 在《Cornetto》三部曲中透露了他最喜欢的电影，这篇文章</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
