-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>根据社区准则的补充， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/twitch">Twitch</a>现已禁止主播在其内容中突出或宣传<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-global-offensive/"><em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》的</em></a>皮肤赌博网站。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/safety-is-never-done-on-twitch-why-the-streaming-giant-is-gearing-up-to-protect-streamers-3306573">“Twitch 上的安全永远不会被忽视”：为什么这家流媒体巨头正准备保护流媒体</a></strong></li></ul><p>Twitch 的<a href="https://safety.twitch.tv/s/article/Community-Guidelines?language=en_US#:~:text=Is%20sponsorship%20of,under%20our%20policy." target="_blank" rel="noopener">社区准则</a>于 8 月 2 日进行了更新以反映这一变化。 “我们的政策禁止宣传或赞助皮肤赌博，”在流媒体服务上是否允许任何游戏中的皮肤赌博问题的答案中写道。</p><p>此外，主播不能“在聊天中分享老虎机网站的推荐代码，包含带有在线轮盘游戏链接的横幅”或“口头将您的聊天推荐到包含骰子游戏的网站”。</p><p>对于此更新的特殊性存在一些困惑。由于它指的是皮肤赌博网站的“推广”或“赞助”，因此 Twitch 主播可能可以使用这些网站展示自己。 </p><figure id="attachment_3477646" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3477646" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3477646" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/counter-strike-global-offensive-skin-gambling-disallowed-on-twitch-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3477646" class="wp-caption-text">一个人在个人电脑上使用键盘 图片来源：Yan Krukau，来自 Pexels</figcaption></figure><p>此外，今年早些时候与这些网站合作的主播和组织可能会受到新要求的影响。 <a href="https://kotaku.com/twitch-bans-csgo-skin-gambling-sponsorships-promo-pc-1850701882"><em>Kotaku</em></a>指出，在 Twitch 上拥有 136,000 名粉丝的全球电子竞技俱乐部<a href="https://www.twitch.tv/g2esports" target="_blank" rel="noopener">G2 Esports</a>于 5 月与 CSGORoll 签订了合同。</p><p>该网站的标志出现在该组织的球衣上，G2 Esports 的选手<a href="https://www.csgoroll.com/en/withdraw/csgo/p2p" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在 CSGORoll 主页上</a>被显示为“官方合作伙伴”。</p><p> <em>《反恐精英：全球攻势》</em>皮肤赌博长期以来一直是热门话题。 2022 年，一位收藏家的皮肤库存被盗， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/1-6-million-worth-of-csgo-skins-stolen-by-hacker-3253446">价值约 160 万英镑的贵重物品被出售</a>或存放在黑客的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/Steam">Steam</a>帐户中。</p><p>皮肤的利润非常丰厚，以至于<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/valve">Valve</a>向焦虑的玩家保证， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/counter-strike-2-wont-take-away-your-csgo-skins-3418940">他们现有的皮肤将转移</a>到<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/counter-strike-2"><em>《反恐精英 2》</em></a>中，并且在技术更优越的续作发布时不会丢失。</p><p>其他游戏新闻方面，根据<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">EA</a>最近的公告， <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/star-wars-jedi-survivor"><em>《星球大战绝地：幸存者》</em></a>未来将可在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/ps4">PlayStation 4</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>上<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/ea-confirms-star-wars-jedi-survivor-is-coming-to-ps4-and-xbox-one-3477541">玩</a>。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/promoting-csgo-gambling-is-prohibited-on-twitch-now-3477609">Twitch 上禁止宣传“CS:GO”赌博的帖子现在</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
