菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers) 在高中时剃光头，看起来像西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O'Connor) https://www.nme.com/news/music/phoebe-bridgers-shaved-her-head-in-high-school-to-look-like-sinead-oconnor-3477499?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=phoebe-布里杰斯在高中时剃光了头发，看起来像西尼德·奥康纳Tom SkinnerThu, 03 Aug 2023 07:55:45 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndiePophttps://www.nme.com/?p=3477499 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sinead O&#39;Connor（左）和 Phoebe Bridgers（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>布里杰斯说，她十几岁的时候就对这位“革命”歌手和活动家“着迷”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phoebe-bridgers-shaved-her-head-in-high-school-to-look-like-sinead-oconnor-3477499">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers) 在高中时剃了光头，看起来就像西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sinead O&#39;Connor（左）和 Phoebe Bridgers（右）在舞台上现场表演的两张并排图像" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/SineadOConnor-Phoebe-Bridgers-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/phoebe-bridgers">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers)</a>透露，她在高中时受到“革命”<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sinead-oconnor">西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>的启发，剃了光头。</p><p>音乐家兼活动家奥康纳<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-irish-music-legend-dies-aged-56-3473863">上周三（7 月 26 日）在伦敦的家中去世</a>。她今年 56 岁。目前死因尚不清楚，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sinead-oconnor-was-found-unresponsive-at-home-police-say-3474196">警方表示，并未将其视为可疑</a>。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/sinead-oconnor-obituary-3473864">Sinéad O&#39;Connor，1966-2023：一位正直、强烈和诚实的艺术家</a></strong></li></ul><p>此后，音乐界的许多人物都表达了敬意，包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/billy-corgan">Billy Corgan</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/michael-stipe">Michael Stipe</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-fall-out-boy-cover-nothing-compares-2-u-in-tribute-to-sinead-oconnor-3474325">Fall Out Boy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-t">Ice-T</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-footage-tori-amos-covers-two-sinead-oconnor-songs-in-tribute-3474641">Tori Amos</a> 。</p><p>在接受<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/phoebe-bridgers-sinead-oconnor-tribute-1234798904/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>滚石杂志</em></a>采访时，独奏家兼<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/boygenius">Boygenius</a>成员布里杰斯回忆起年轻时第一次了解奥康纳的音乐、生活和信仰。她告诉该刊物，听到她去世的消息她感到“心碎”。</p><p> “我第一次听到她的声音可能要感谢我的妈妈，她曾经并且仍然拥有最酷的音乐品味，”布里杰斯解释道。</p><p> “甚至在我听到 Sinéad 的音乐之前，我就知道她是一位革命者。我对她和《Nothing Compares 2 U》视频着迷。”</p><p>她继续说道：“我什至在高中时就剃了一个非常非常短的头。我绝对是给她剃的。我的头型最差，所以我愿意剃光头的人并不多。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Phoebe Bridgers - Black Boys On Mopeds（Sinéad O&#39;connor 封面）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kVwMsGhEWyM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>这位音乐家接着回忆起她后来如何“开始深入研究[奥康纳]和她所代表的东西”，并补充道：“[……]西妮德总是相信她真正相信的事情，而不是别人<em>告诉</em>她要相信的事情，即使它是完全颠覆性的。”</p><p>布里杰斯随后特别推荐了《骑轻便摩托车的黑人男孩》，这是一首在英国黑人科林·罗奇去世后创作的政治歌曲。虽然歌词没有直接提及罗奇，但这首歌讲述了警察的暴行，奥康纳将她的专辑“I Do Not Want What I Haven&#39;t Got”献给了他的家人。</p><p>这首歌以关于时任首相玛格丽特·撒切尔的台词开头，此前曾由布里杰斯翻唱过。</p><p> “这是一个非常简单的录音，”布里杰斯谈到原始版本时说道。 “翻唱[奥康纳]的好处在于，她让最难唱的事情听起来变得如此简单。我必须大量练习《骑轻便摩托车的黑人男孩》，甚至还制作了一个白痴版本。她的声音风格与众不同。” </p><figure id="attachment_3473873" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3473873" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3473873" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header.jpg" alt="1988 年 Sinead O&#39;Connor 在舞台上现场表演的黑白照片" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Sinead-O-Connor-header-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3473873" class="wp-caption-text">爱尔兰歌手 Sinead O&#39;Connor 于 1988 年 3 月 16 日在荷兰阿姆斯特丹 Paradiso 表演。图片来源：Paul Bergen/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/sinead-oconnor-talks-infamous-snl-performance-in-new-trailer-for-nothing-compares-documentary-3311426">1992 年，在臭名昭著的<em>SNL</em>节目</a>中，奥康纳在翻唱鲍勃·马利 (Bob Marley) 的《战争》(War) 时撕毁了一张教皇的照片，并用“虐待儿童”取代了歌曲歌词中的“种族主义”。她以“与真正的敌人战斗”结束表演，随后解释说此举是为了抗议天主教堂中的儿童性虐待行为。</p><p>布里杰斯告诉<em>《滚石》杂志</em>：“无论是关于饥荒、天主教会还是玛格丽特·撒切尔，历史都站在她一边，但在当时却并非如此。人们和媒体对她并不友善。”</p><p>这位歌手说奥康纳“被很多事情所排斥”，并补充道：“这是一个如此悲伤和令人心碎的故事。 [……]她为女性、音乐家和相信事物的人们做出了巨大的牺牲。她因此没有得到任何回报。”</p><p>布里杰斯的言论与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lily-allen">莉莉·艾伦</a>的言论相呼应，莉莉·艾伦<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lily-allen-incensed-by-spineless-tributes-to-sinead-oconnor-3475673">表示，她对一些对奥康纳的“无骨气”的致敬感到“愤怒”</a> ，暗示这些人在她活着的时候不会为奥康纳挺身而出。</p><p>艾伦补充道：“同样令人不安的是，人们似乎对她非常同情，但出于某种原因却觉得自己无法表现出来或表达出来。直到他们去世。这对我们来说意味着什么？”</p><p>与此同时，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/morrissey">莫里西</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/morrissey-attacks-music-industry-following-sinead-oconnors-death-3474159">批评了音乐界对奥康纳去世的反应</a>。这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-smiths">史密斯</a>乐队主唱辩称，有些人的评论是“虚伪的”，因为他们“没有勇气在她活着的时候支持她，而她正在寻找你”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/phoebe-bridgers-shaved-her-head-in-high-school-to-look-like-sinead-oconnor-3477499">菲比·布里杰斯 (Phoebe Bridgers) 在高中时剃了光头，看起来就像西妮德·奥康纳 (Sinéad O&#39;Connor)</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 NewJeans 击败《芭比娃娃》原声带首次登上 Billboard 200 排行榜第一名https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-beat-barbie-soundtrack-debut-number-one-billboard-200-3477500?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=newjeans-beat-barbie-soundtrack-debut-第一广告牌 200Puah Ziwei Thu, 03 Aug 2023 07:36:05 +0000 Music NewsNewsK-pop https://www.nme.com/?p=3477500 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Newjeans 首次亮相广告牌 200 玛格特·罗比芭比第一名" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> They are the second K-pop girl group to top the chart, after BLACKPINK</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-beat-barbie-soundtrack-debut-number-one-billboard-200-3477500">NewJeans beat out &#39;Barbie&#39; soundtrack to debut at Number One on the Billboard 200</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="newjeans debut number one billboard 200 margot robbie barbie" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/08/newjeans-margot-robbie-barbie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> K-pop girl group <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/newjeans">NewJeans</a> have earned their first chart-topping album on the Billboard 200 with their <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-get-up-asap-music-video-release-3473520">sophomore release &#39;Get Up&#39;</a> , besting the all-star <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>Barbie</em></a> soundtrack.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE: <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/newjeans-get-up-review-3471523">NewJeans – &#39;Get Up&#39; review: no one can hold a candle to K-pop&#39;s rising wonder girls</a></strong></li></ul><p> <a href="https://www.billboard.com/music/chart-beat/newjeans-get-up-number-one-billboard-200-1235383894/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Billboard</a> recently announced the ranked for the latest Billboard 200 chart, for the week of August 5, 2023. NewJeans entered the chart for the first time with &#39;Get Up&#39;, which also debuted at Number One on the list. The quintet are the second K-pop girl group to do so, following <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blackpink">BLACKPINK</a> last September with &#39;Born Pink&#39;.</p><p> According to Billboard, &#39;Get Up&#39; earned 126,500 equivalent album units in the US for the charting week, with a large number of the figure being driven by physical sales of the album. Meanwhile, streaming equivalent albums accounted for 24,500 units, which equals to around 34million on-demand official streams of the mini-album&#39;s six tracks.</p><p> NewJeans are the third K-pop act to top the Billboard 200 in 2023. In June, <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stray-kids">Stray Kids</a> scored their <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stray-kids-billboard-200-number-one-5-star-3454520">third-straight chart-topping release with &#39;5-Star&#39;</a> , while Tomorrow x Together clinched their <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/tomorrow-x-together-txt-first-billboard-200-number-one-name-chapter-temptation-3394433">first with &#39;The Name Chapter: Temptation&#39; in February</a> .</p><p> Meanwhile, the <em>Barbie</em> soundtrack – which features songs from <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dua-lipa">Dua Lipa</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicki-minaj">Nicki Minaj</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/fifty-fifty">FIFTY FIFTY</a> and more – debuted at Number Two with 126,000 equivalent album units. Notably, that&#39;s the biggest week for a <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album-review-a-star-is-born-official-soundtrack-2387517">film soundtrack since <em>A Star is Born</em></a> by <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lady-gaga">Lady Gaga</a> and Bradley Cooper in March 2019, following the Academy Awards in February.</p><p> The <em>Barbie</em> soundtrack also recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/barbie-soundtrack-makes-history-on-uk-singles-chart-3475296">made history on UK singles chart</a> with the most amount of songs ever in a Top Five. Elsewhere, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/greta-gerwig-listened-to-dua-lipas-barbie-song-100-times-in-one-morning-3474762">Greta Gerwig listened to Dua Lipa&#39;s <em>Barbie</em> song &#39;Dance The Night&#39; “100 times” in one morning</a> , according to Mark Ronson.</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newjeans-beat-barbie-soundtrack-debut-number-one-billboard-200-3477500">NewJeans beat out &#39;Barbie&#39; soundtrack to debut at Number One on the Billboard 200</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
